My mate was part of the film crew, and he told me some juicy spoilers. Apparently Bond's going to have ants up his arse in this new film. At first he thinks it's some kind of fiendishly clever tech, until a big reveal where ants come crawling out of his arse, much to Bond's fascination and horror.

He's also going to catch genital warts from Ms Moneypenny, very big, bright purple ones that will look like he's got a bunch of grapes dangling between his legs.

M is going to get caught bothering other men in the office toilets, which will lead to a fight with the office gopher, who will give M a thorough pasting before doing a runner and becoming the film's baddie.

The facial scarring is apparently from making contact with M's genital warts when he thrust his junk into his face during the clumsy sexual offer-turned frenzied scuffle.

So it's all sounding tremendously exciting, I must say.
